      <div class="about-content">
        <section>
          <h3>Our Story</h3>
          <p>Welcome to Pizza Palace, where authentic Italian flavors meet Berlin's vibrant culinary scene. Founded in 2010 by Chef Marco Rossi, we've been serving the finest Neapolitan-style pizzas in the heart of Berlin. Our journey began with a simple wood-fired oven and a passion for traditional Italian cooking techniques.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>Our Values</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Authentic Italian Recipes</li>
            <li>Locally-Sourced Ingredients</li>
            <li>Traditional Wood-Fired Cooking</li>
            <li>Warm, Welcoming Atmosphere</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>Our Team</h3>
          <p>Our team of passionate chefs, led by Chef Marco, brings years of experience from Italy's finest pizzerias. Each pizza is crafted with care, using traditional techniques passed down through generations. We're proud to bring a taste of Italy to Berlin's diverse food scene.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3>Our Location</h3>
          <p>Located in the heart of Berlin's Mitte district, our restaurant offers a cozy atmosphere perfect for family dinners, romantic dates, or casual gatherings. Our outdoor seating area is particularly popular during Berlin's beautiful summer evenings.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

